name: Ted Fox  CD album
description:
2006-2010 : La période Ted Fox est remplie par cet album, illustré par Thierry Rouquet, auteur de BD.
Cet album est de l'indy folk issue tout droit du passé Hardcore de Ted fox.
Aucune rythmique, aucune basse, Seulement des guitares et des voix.

DIGIPAK-livret 12 pages.
Lyrics, Music & album-design par Ted fox


En 2011, Ted Fox devient Yel Fox. 
_______________________________


2006-2010 : Ted Fox period is filled by this album, The booklet artwork is by Thierry Rouquet, Comic author.
This album is an Indy folk inspired by the Rock-Hardcore past of Ted fox.
No drums, no bass, Only guitars and voices.
DIGIPAK-10 pages booklet .
Lyrics, Music & album-design by Ted fox

In 2011, Ted Fox becomes Yel Fox.
